OL,3,CTranmere Rovers sack manager Andy
OL,4,CCrosby after run of losses
OL,6,FTranmere Rovers have sacked their
OL,7,Fmanager after a run of losses.
OL,9,FUnder Andy Crosby, the Rovers have
OL,10,Flost ten of their last 11 matches and
OL,11,Fhave now slipped to 19th in the League
OL,12,FTwo table.
OL,14,FOn Sunday 1 March, they suffered a 3-1
OL,15,Fdefeat to relegation-threatened
OL,16,FNewport.
OL,18,FFirst Team coach Andy Parkinson will
OL,19,Ftake interim control, while Connor
OL,20,FJennings has been promoted to
OL,21,Fassistant.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
