CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772651488
OL,3,CTranmere Rovers sack manager Andy
OL,4,CCrosby after run of losses
OL,6,FChairman Mark Palios said in a
OL,7,Fstatement: "Andy did a great job for
OL,8,Fus last year and has undoubtedly been
OL,9,Fdealt a tough hand this season with
OL,10,Fthe exceptionally high level of
OL,11,Finjuries we have experienced.
OL,13,F"However, I felt a change was
OL,14,Funfortunately necessary to try to
OL,15,Faddress the poor run of results. I
OL,16,Fhave no doubt that Andy has put his
OL,17,Fall into the role over the last 12
OL,18,Fmonths in difficult circumstances and
OL,19,FI wish him all the best for the
OL,20,Ffuture."
OL,26,@oD@LOUuD@AOU|D@HO]
