PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772651488
OL,3,CTranmere Rovers sack manager Andy
OL,4,CCrosby after run of losses
OL,6,FCrosby was celebrated by supporters
OL,7,Flast season after he was credited from
OL,8,Fsaving the club when he came in as
OL,9,Finterim manager.
OL,11,FUnder him the Rovers finished 20th and
OL,12,Fnine points clear of relegation.
OL,14,FPrior to his sacking, Tranmere Rovers'
OL,15,FOfficial Supporters' Club had called,
OL,16,Fexternal for an "immediate change" to
OL,17,Fthe managerial team, saying Crosby's
OL,18,Fposition was "untenable".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
