PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772651488
OL,3,CTranmere Rovers sack manager Andy
OL,4,CCrosby after run of losses
OL,6,FFollowing their loss on Sunday, Crosby
OL,7,Fsaid: "As the manager of the football
OL,8,Fclub the run we're on is my
OL,9,Fresponsibility.
OL,11,F"But I'm a big boy and I'll keep doing
OL,12,Feverything I possibly can to change
OL,13,Fthis run around. I'm giving absolutely
OL,14,Feverything."
